### Chapter 8. RACI Governance Framework
- **Responsible (R)** : Performs the work
- **Accountable (A)** : Ultimately answerable for outcome
- **Consulted (C)** : Provides expert input before decisions
- **Informed (I)** : Receives updates after decisions

**Example RACI Matrix:**
| Activity | CEO | CTO | CAIO | CRO | COO | Treasury | Compliance | Internal Audit |
|----------|-----|-----|------|-----|-----|----------|------------|----------------|
| Trading Strategy Approval | A | C | C | C | R | I | I | I |
| AI Model Deployment | I | A | R | C | C | I | I | I |
| Capital Allocation | I | I | C | C | C | A/R | I | I |
| Risk Limit Approval | A | I | C | R | C | I | C | I |
| Wallet Governance | I | C | I | C | I | A/R | C | I |
| Security Incident Response | I | A | I | C | R | I | I | C |
| Internal Audit Plan | I | I | I | C | I | I | C | A/R |

